para_trans: Deputy Superintendent of Land Records, Group 'B' from Group 'C' Post-II of the Land Records Department.
Posts by Temporary Promotion in the Cadre
Government Order No: Promotion - 0823 / P.No.356 / E-6
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
Read: 1) GOVERNMENT NOTICE, GENERAL ADMINISTRATION DEPARTMENT, SRV-2020 / Q. No.49 / ACTION.12, Dated 14.07.2021.
2) Government Order, Revenue & Forest Department, No. Promotion - 0823 / P.S. No.356 / E-6,

GOVERNMENT ORDER: The following employees, who have qualified from the selection list of S.N. 2022-23 in the cadre of Group 'C' Post-II of the Land Records Department, have been appointed as Deputy Superintendents of Land Records, Group 'B' (Pay Scale S - 15-41800-132300) in the cadre of Read No. Read Government Order No. 2. Revenue Division Allocation as per the provision in the notification in 1.
Mr. Pradeep Bandopant Gaikwad, an employee of Section 47 of the said order, has been temporarily promoted to the post of Columnist.
The post was established at the place mentioned in 4. Now Mr. Pradeep Bandopant in this order
Gaekwad is being given a revised posting as mentioned in Column 5, with a partial change in the posting given by his promotion.
2. Read No. The other terms and conditions of the Government Order dated 04.12.2023 in Section 2 shall remain the same.
The Government Order is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
